speech: People call me Terry Tulip. What else would you like to know?
Cathy Cactus. But ask me something else please?
I was called Daan, and then I changed my name to Bram. Now, I go by Luuk. Any other questions?
Mila. Ask me something else now?
I used to be called Lotte, except no one could say it right. So, I now go by Anna. Any other questions?
